  "title": "Delivery Driver",
  "description": "<p>Puricare Pte Ltd</p><p>Delivery Driver (Class 3/4)<br /><br />Job Description</p><p>· Assist in loading and unloading<br />· Ensure safe and timely delivery of items<br />· Collection of receipts and payments if any<br />· Meeting delivery deadline<br />· Take care of the vehicle<br />· Assist in the preparation of equipment before delivery<br />· Assist in Service Centre repairing work<br />. Ad hoc duties as per assigned by Supervisor</p><p>Requirements:<br />* Min 1-2 years of working experience<br />* Good communication, independent, committed, full of initiative<br />* Bilingual in spoken languages<br />* must be physically strong<br />* Possess driving license (4 manual)<br />* Able to work overtime on Saturday (at times required)</p><p>Interested candidate may send in their resume either via email to: hr@puricare.com.sg or Whatsapp to: 96518935</p>",
